:::'''Laojiu:''' A Xianzhou citizen will never lie to another Xianzhou citizen... Oh wait, you're not from the Xianzhou.
:::'''Laojiu:''' But you can still rest assured that my prices are completely transparent and fully refundable if you are dissatisfied with my service.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Truthfully, you might not have the seat that I want...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502130007-->
:::'''Laojiu:''' Oh! It seems like we have ourselves a rich client. Well, there's no seat in this world that I cannot get. It just depends on how much you are willing to spend!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Don't tickets require real-name registration nowadays?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502130009-->
:::'''Laojiu:''' Think about it this way. Real-name registration is only required for audiences with tickets. For those without tickets, why would they need to register their names?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502130010-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502130010-->
::'''Laojiu:''' Well, let me introduce myself. I'm Laojiu, the vendor for the special viewing channel. This special viewing channel is a specially designed solution for people like you who has the money but did not manage to get tickets.
::'''Laojiu:''' As of today, I have served hundreds of satisfied clients and have 100% success rate and positive reviews.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Aren't you just a scalper?
