::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Save your explanation for the Realm-Keeping Commission.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502130015-->
:::'''Laojiu:''' Why are people nowadays so heartless, doing things that harm others even though it doesn't benefit them... You could always just not buy from me.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502130016-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502130016-->
::'''Laojiu:''' Actually, I can also tell that you're not interested in the competition. What about making money? I'm sure you're interested in that.
